Get a dataframe of multiple draws of only the predicted elements of the nowcast vector

Usage

get_nowcast_pred_draws(point_nowcast_pred_matrix, disp, n_draws = 1000)

Arguments

point_nowcast_pred_matrix

Matrix containing only the elements that have not yet been observed as of the final reference date.

disp

Vector of dispersion parameters indexed by horizon from minus one to the maximum delay.

n_draws

Integer indicating the number of draws of the predicted nowcast vector to generate. Default is 1000.

Value

Dataframe containing the predicted point nowcast vectors indexed by reference time (pred_count), reference time (time), and the draw index (draw).
